tags.description: Please do NOT add a turning circle or mini roundabout; I have cycled past it multiple times recently and it has turned into two lanes with a turn lane from Lots Road to the North to Harbour Avenue to the South. This message is to the mappers   who may be

I believe the purpose of this dropped kerb, with the shared space directly to the north is to facilitate joining Eel Brook Common for northbound cyclists from WBR. 
Southbound, joining WBR is possible, but hairy. (use ASL but beware of left-filter)
